data.form:
<script>
   window.App.IndexController.reopen({
         arrivals: [
              {'Bus':'1254', 'Time':'2:35PM', 'Open Seats':'10'}
             ],
        busStops: Ember.computed(function() {
            var facts = this.get("facts");
            var locations2 = this.get("busLocations");
            var calculatedStops = new Array();
            for ( var i = 0, l = locations2.length; i < l; i++ ) {
                calculatedStops.push({
                    lat: locations2[i].lat,
                    lng: locations2[i].lng
                });
            }
            Ember.set(facts, "calculatedStops", calculatedStops);
            return calculatedStops;
        }),
        busLocations: Ember.computed(function() {
            var facts = this.get("facts");
            var busStops = Ember.A();
            if (facts.apidata_data.results) {
                console.log(facts.apidata_data.results)
                facts.apidata_data.results.bus.forEach( function(data) {
                    var busLatLong = Ember.A();
                    busLatLong[0] = parseFloat(data.lat);
                    busLatLong[1] = parseFloat(data.lng);
                    console.log(busLatLong);
                    busStops.pushObject(busLatLong);
                    console.log("HELLO");
               });
            } else {
                var busLatLong = Ember.A();
                console.log("GOODBYE");
                busLatLong[0] = parseFloat(facts.apidata_data.results.bus.lat);
                busLatLong[1] = parseFloat(facts.apidata_data.results.bus.lng);
                busStops.pushObject(busLatLong);
            }
            Ember.set(facts, "busStops", busStops);
            
            var newStuff = Ember.A();
            for(var i=0; i<facts.busStops.length; i++) {
                var stop = facts.busStops[i];
                var content2 = {lat: stop[0],lng: stop[1]};
                console.log(content2)
                newStuff.pushObject(content2);
            }
            Ember.set(facts, "newStuff", newStuff);
            return newStuff;
        }),
        endpoints: Ember.computed(function() {
             var facts = this.get("facts");
            //  return [[{lat:39.956488,lng:-75.192249}, {lat:39.956580,lng:-75.190041}]];
             return [[{lat:facts.newStuff[0].lat,lng:facts.newStuff[0].lng}, {lat:facts.newStuff[(facts.newStuff.length)-1].lat,lng:facts.newStuff[(facts.newStuff.length)-1].lng}]];
        }),
        actions: {
            goDirection: function() {
                console.log("trying to GO!");
            },
            openMapsApp: function(){
                var facts = this.get("facts");
                console.log(facts.calculatedStops[0].lat);
                console.log(facts.calculatedStops[0].lng);
                window.location.href = 'comgooglemaps://?q='+facts.calculatedStops[0].lat+','+facts.calculatedStops[0].lng+'&zoom=14';
            }
        }
   });
</script>

<script type="text/x-handlebars" data-template-name="index">
    {{sc-map locations=controller.busLocations waypoints=controller.busStops endpoints=controller.endpoints height='100%' width='100%' zoom=12}}
</script>

<script>
   
     function initMap() {
       var map = new google.maps.Map(document.getElementById('map'), {
         center: {lat: -34.397, lng: 150.644},
         zoom: 11
       });
       
      var infoWindow = new google.maps.InfoWindow({map: map});
       
      if (navigator.geolocation) {
         navigator.geolocation.getCurrentPosition(function(position) {
          var pos = {
             lat: position.coords.latitude,
             lng: position.coords.longitude
          };

          infoWindow.setPosition(pos);
          infoWindow.setContent('You are here.');
          map.setCenter(pos);
         }, function() {
          handleLocationError(true, infoWindow, map.getCenter());
         });
      } else {
         handleLocationError(false, infoWindow, map.getCenter());
      }
      
      // setting the markers on the Map
      setMarkers(map);
     }

   function handleLocationError(browserHasGeolocation, infoWindow, pos) {
       infoWindow.setPosition(pos);
       infoWindow.setContent(browserHasGeolocation ?
                             'Error: The Geolocation service failed.' :
                             'Error: Your browser doesn\'t support geolocation.');
     }

   </script>
</body>
